name: Da Varanda #024
description: This is the twenty-fourth photo, size 2000 x 3008 px - ISO 200 | 28mm | f/4,5 | 1/800 sec. One week, an apartment balcony and a camera. This series of photos is being produced from the balcony of my apartment. For 1 week, I will photograph the life that I can see from up here on the 10th floor. All will be minted in 100 editions at a low price and after the sale period, those that are not sold will be burned.
